Speaker 1: However, if you wanted, I'd be happy to send you the AGVs free to try.

Speaker 2: So I could get you a sample of it to make up for that, and I could put your account on a pause.

Speaker 1: You can see if the AGVs work differently for you.

Speaker 2: And then you could give me a call back and let me know how you want to proceed.

Speaker 1: Can I do that? I'll try the trial run and see what happens with it.

Speaker 2: Yeah, so just know that's good. You're going to get two orders, okay? So the first one that's going to be delivered will be the—

Speaker 1: Standard generics that the script was written for. Okay, the second item that you're going to receive will be the AGV one.

Speaker 2: The way you're going to tell the model is AGV is it will say sildenafil AGV on the front on the bottom right-hand corner.

Speaker 1: It will say Greenstone LLC.

Speaker 2: Greenstone is the Pfizer labs in France. Okay, the ones you're getting right now are from Apco Pharma in New Jersey.

Speaker 1: So there's the big difference, and the pills themselves will have 100 on it where you say AC 320 or another generic code.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: I'll give it a shot.

Speaker 2: Yeah, give these a try. I can also provide you with my extension so you can call me back directly. Would you like that?

Speaker 1: Uh, well, I'm on the run, so I don't have pen and paper with me. Okay. I don't know if you can send me—

Speaker 2: Send me a text or send a text, but if you do that, I'll take information on the text.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I'm unable to send a text, but it's just zero zero four two. So 42 is my extension and my name—

Speaker 2: But like I said, I'll send you that sample to make up for all, you know—

Speaker 1: These and see if we can get you something that works a little bit better. Okay, so this will be 10—

Speaker 1: Okay, I appreciate it. I'm willing to try. Thank you.

Speaker 2: Yep. You're very welcome. Thank you.
